(thirdQuint)Pilot Study of Paclitaxel Plus Pembrolizumab in Metastatic HER2-Negative Breast Cancer.

 This is an open-label randomized pilot research study to determine if the study drug, pembrolizumab, is safe to use in combination with a chemotherapy drug called paclitaxel.

 This study will have the following two regimens: Cohort A) phased regimen of pembrolizumab in which paclitaxel is followed by paclitaxel plus pembrolizumab and Cohort B) concurrent regimen of paclitaxel plus pembrolizumab.

 A total of 40 evaluable subjects will be enrolled over an enrollment period of 18-24 months.

 The study is planned to enroll approximately 20 evaluable subjects in each treatment cohort.

