The primary objective of this study is to assess the safety and feasibility of the following two regimens: Cohort A) phased regimen of pembrolizumab in which paclitaxel is followed by paclitaxel plus pembrolizumab and Cohort B) concurrent regimen of paclitaxel plus pembrolizumab.

 The primary safety objective is to evaluate the overall grade 3 or 4 treatment-related adverse event rate for each cohort and compare them to relevant historical controls.

